\c 4
\s Amafutha omfelokazi
\p
\v 1 Kwasekukhala kuElisha umfazi othile wabafazi bamadodana abaprofethi\x + 2.3.\x* esithi: Inceku yakho umkami sewafa; lawe uyazi ukuthi inceku yakho yayiyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd*; sekufikile umkweledisi ukuzithathela abantwana bami ababili babe yizigqili\x + 1 Sam. 22.2. Levi 25.39-41. Neh. 5.5. Mat. 18.25.\x*.
\v 2 UElisha wasesithi kuye: Ngi\add nga\add*kwenzelani? Ngitshela, ulani endlini? Wasesithi: Incekukazi yakho kayilalutho endlini, ngaphandle kwesiphiso samafutha.
\v 3 Wasesithi: Hamba u\add ye\add*zebolekela izitsha ezivela phandle, kubomakhelwane bakho bonke, izitsha ezingelalutho, zingabi nlutshwana\x + 6.5. Eks. 3.22. 11.2. 12.35.\x*.
\v 4 Nxa usungenile uzivalele wena lamadodana akho umnyango, uthele kulezizitsha zonke; lokugcweleyo ukubeke eceleni.
\v 5 Wasesuka-ke kuye wazivalela yena lamadodana akhe umnyango; bazisondeza kuye, wathulula.
\v 6 Kwasekusithi izitsha sezigcwele wathi endodaneni yakhe: Ngilethela njalo isitsha. Yasisithi kuye: Kakuselasitsha. Amafutha asesima.
\v 7 Wasesiza wamazisa umuntu kaNkulunkulu; wasesithi: Hamba u\add ye\add*thengisa amafutha, uhlawule isikwelede sakho; wena-ke lamadodana akho liphile ngaseleyo\x + Hlu. 13.6. 1 Kho. 17.16.\x*.
\s UElisha lowesifazana weShunemi
\p
\v 8 Kwasekusithi ngo\add lunye\add* usuku uElisha wedlulela eShunemi\x + Josh. 19.18.\x* lapho okwakulowesifazana oyisikhulu\x + 1 Sam. 25.2. 2 Sam. 19.32.\x* owamcindezela ukuthi adle isinkwa. Kwakusithi-ke lanini esedlula, aphambukele khona ukuthi adle isinkwa.
\v 9 Wasesithi kumkakhe: Khangela-ke, ngiyazi ukuthi lo ungumuntu ongcwele kaNkulunkulu, owedlula kithi njalonjalo\x + Hlu. 13.6. 1 Kho. 17.16.\x*.
\v 10 Ake senze ikamelo elincinyane eliphezulu emdulini\x + Hlu. 3.20.\x*, simfakele lapho umbheda letafula lesihlalo lesiqobane sesibane; kuzakuthi-ke lapho efika kithi aphambukele khona.
\p
\v 11 Kwasekusithi ngo\add lunye\add* usuku wafika khona, waphambukela ekamelweni eliphezulu, walala khona\x + Hlu. 3.20.\x*.
\v 12 Wasesithi kuGehazi inceku yakhe\x + 14,25. 5.20. 8.4,5.\x*: Biza lo umShunamikazi\x + Josh. 19.18.\x*. Esembizile, wema phambi kwakhe.
\v 13 Wasesithi kuyo: Tshono kuye-ke \add uthi\add*: Khangela, usinakekele ngakho konke lokhukunaka\x + 1 Sam. 16.4.\x*; kuyini ongakwenzelwa? Kukhona ongakukhulunyelwa enkosini kumbe enduneni yebutho yini\x + 5.1. 2 Sam. 19.13.\x*? Wasesithi: Ngihlala phakathi kwabantu bakithi.
\v 14 Wasesithi: Kuyini-ke angakwenzelwa? UGehazi wasesithi: Qiniso, kalamntwana, lomkakhe u\add se\add*mdala.
\v 15 Wasesithi: Mbize. Esembizile, wema emnyango.
\v 16 Wasesithi: Ngalesisikhathi esimisiweyo njengokwesikhathi sempilo\x + Gen. 18.14.\x* uzagona umntwana\x + Gen. 29.13. 33.4. 48.10.\x*. Kodwa wathi: Hatshi, nkosi yami, muntu kaNkulunkulu\x + Hlu. 13.6. 1 Kho. 17.16.\x*, ungayiqambeli amanga incekukazi yakho\x + 4.28.\x*.
\v 17 Owesifazana wasekhulelwa, wabeletha umntwana ngalesosikhathi esimisiweyo njengokwesikhathi sempilo uElisha ayesitshilo kuye.
\p
\v 18 Esekhulile umntwana, kwathi ngosuku \add oluthile\add* waphuma waya kuyise kubavuni.
\v 19 Wasesithi kuyise: Ikhanda lami! Ikhanda lami! Wasesithi encekwini: Mthwale umuse kunina\x + Hlab. 121.6.\x*.
\v 20 Isimthwele yamusa kunina, wahlala emadolweni akhe kwaze kwaba semini, wasesifa.
\v 21 Wasesenyuka, wamlalisa embhedeni\x + 4.10,32.\x* womuntu kaNkulunkulu\x + Hlu. 13.6. 1 Kho. 17.16.\x*, wamvalela, waphuma\x + 4.4,5,33.\x*.
\v 22 Wasememeza umkakhe wathi: Ake uthume kimi enye yezinceku lomunye wabobabhemi, ukuze ngigijime ngiye emuntwini kaNkulunkulu, ngibuye futhi\x + Hlu. 13.6. 1 Kho. 17.16.\x*.
\v 23 Wasesithi. Uyelani kuye lamuhla? Kakusikuthwasa kwenyanga njalo kakusisabatha\x + Nani 28.11.\x*. \add Owesifazana\add* wasesithi: Kulungile.
\v 24 Esembophelele isihlalo ubabhemi, wathi encekwini yakhe: Tshaya uhambe, ungangibambeleli ekuhambeni, ngaphandle ngikutshele.
\v 25 Wahamba-ke, weza emuntwini kaNkulunkulu entabeni iKharmeli\x + 2.25. Josh. 19.26.\x*. Kwasekusithi umuntu kaNkulunkulu embona esiza\x + 2.7.\x*, wathi kuGehazi inceku yakhe: Khangela, \add nangu\add*yana umShunamikazi\x + Josh. 19.18.\x*.
\v 26 Khathesi akugijime umhlangabeze, uthi kuye: Kulungile yini kuwe? Kulungile yini ngomkakho? Kulungile yini ngomntwana? Wasesithi: Kulungile.
\v 27 Esefikile entabeni\x + 4.25.\x* kumuntu kaNkulunkulu wabamba inyawo zakhe. Kodwa uGehazi wasondela ukumsunduza asuke\x + Mat. 28.9.\x*. Kodwa umuntu kaNkulunkulu wathi: Myekele, ngoba umphefumulo wakhe umunyu kuye, leN\nd kosi\nd* ingifihlele \add lokhu\add*, kayingitshelanga.
\v 28 Wasesithi: Ngangicelile indodana enkosini yami yini? Kangitshongo yini \add ukuthi\add*: Ungangikhohlisi\x + 4.16.\x*?
\v 29 \add UElisha\add* wasesithi kuGehazi: Bopha ukhalo lwakho, uthathe udondolo lwami esandleni sakho, uhambe\x + 1 Kho. 18.46.\x*. Uba uhlangana lomuntu ungambingeleli, njalo uba umuntu ekubingelela ungamphenduli\x + Luka 10.4. 1 Sam. 13.10.\x*; ubeke udondolo lwami ebusweni bomntwana\x + 2.21. Seb. 19.12.\x*.
\v 30 Unina womntwana wasesithi: Kuphila kukaJehova lokuphila komphefumulo wakho, kangiyikukutshiya\x + 2.2. 1 Sam. 1.26. 20.3.\x*. Wasesukuma wamlandela.
\p
\v 31 UGehazi wedlulela phambi kwabo, walubeka udondolo ebusweni bomntwana, kodwa kakubanga khona ilizwi njalo kwakungelakunaka. Wasebuyela ukumhlangabeza, wamtshela esithi: Umntwana kavukanga\x + Joha. 11.11.\x*.
\v 32 UElisha esengenile endlini, khangela, umntwana wayefile, elaliswe embhedeni wakhe.
\v 33 Wasengena, wavala umnyango emva kwabo bobabili\x + 4.4. Mat. 6.6. 9.25. Mark. 5.37,40. Luka 8.51,54.\x*, wakhuleka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 1 Kho. 17.20,21.\x*.
\v 34 Wenyuka walala phezu komntwana, wabeka umlomo wakhe phezu komlomo wakhe lamehlo akhe phezu kwamehlo akhe lezandla zakhe phezu kwezandla zakhe, wacambalala phezu kwakhe; inyama yomntwana yasikhudumala\x + 1 Kho. 18.42. 1 Kho. 17.21. Seb. 20.10.\x*.
\v 35 Wasebuyela, wahambahamba endlini waya kanye ngapha lakanye le, wasesenyuka wacambalala phezu kwakhe; umntwana wasethimula kwaze kwaba kasikhombisa, umntwana wasevula amehlo akhe\x + 1 Kho. 18.42. 1 Kho. 17.21. Seb. 20.10.\x*.
\v 36 Wasebiza uGehazi wathi: Mbize lo umShunamikazi\x + 4.4. Mat. 6.6. 9.25. Mark. 5.37,40. Luka 8.51,54.\x*. Wasembiza. Esefikile kuye, wathi kuye: Thatha umntanakho.
\v 37 Wasengena, wawela ezinyaweni zakhe, wakhothamela emhlabathini, waphakamisa umntanakhe, waphuma\x + 8.1,5. 1 Kho. 17.23. Heb. 11.35.\x*.
\s Izimangaliso zikaElisha
\p
\v 38 UElisha wasebuyela eGiligali\x + 2.1.\x*, njalo kwakukhona indlala elizweni\x + 8.1.\x*, amadodana abaprofethi\x + 4.1. 2.3.\x* ayehlezi-ke phambi kwakhe\x + 2.3,5. Dute. 33.3. Luka 10.39. Seb. 22.3.\x*, wathi encekwini yakhe: Beka imbiza enkulu \add eziko\add*, uphekele abaprofethi ukudla okuphekiweyo\x + Hez. 24.3.\x*.
\v 39 Omunye wasephuma waya egangeni ukukha imibhida, wathola intandela yeganga, wakha amajodwana ayo eganga, isembatho sakhe sagcwala, weza wawaqobelela embizeni yokudla okuphekiweyo, ngoba ayengawazi.
\v 40 Basebethululela abantu ukuze badle; kwasekusithi besadla okokudla okuphekiweyo bona bamemeza \add bathi\add*: Ukufa embizeni, muntu kaNkulunkulu! Njalo babengelakukudla.
\v 41 Wasesithi: Lethani-ke impuphu. Waseyithela embizeni wathi: Thululela abantu, ukuze badle. Kwakungaselalutho oluyingozi embizeni\x + 2.21.\x*.
\p
\v 42 Kwasekufika umuntu evela eBhali-Shalisha\x + 1 Sam. 9.4.\x*, walethela umuntu kaNkulunkulu ukudla kwezithelo zokuqala, izinkwa \w zebhali\w** ezingamatshumi amabili\x + 1 Sam. 9.7.\x*, lezikhwebu zamabele amatsha emgodleni wakhe\x + Levi 2.14.\x*. Wasesithi: Banike abantu ukuze badle\x + Mat. 14.16-21. 15.32-38. Mark. 6.37-44. 8.4-9. Luka 9.13-17. Joha. 6.5-13.\x*.
\v 43 Kodwa inceku yakhe yathi: Ini, ngibeke lokhu phambi kwabantu abalikhulu\x + 6.15.\x*? Wasesithi: Banike abantu ukuze badle, ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Bazakudla, batshiye\x + Ruthe 2.14.\x*.
\v 44 Yasikubeka phambi kwabo, badla, batshiya, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Ruthe 2.14.\x*.